channel.title: Registering Help ! D:
channel.description:
I register on the Server Status and put in all my details and it says this :
Error: The server Habby-Live is offline, it must be online before you can register it here.
So I go on the start page and click Start Server and it says that my server has started and then I go back and do it again and nothing happens
Also the Login bit of the main page says Error connecting and when I go on Edit my Server it comes up with :
Error: You have not posted a server, but you may register a new one instead.
Need help on how to register , How to turn it Online and Register it.
Thanks :)

@X_Entinity_X wrote:

You didn’t portforward correctly?, your ports may not be open or your Firewall could be in the way.
